# shadcn instructions

Use the latest version of Shadcn to install new components, like this command to add a button component:

```bash
pnpm dlx shadcn@latest add button
```

# TanStack Intent

When working on TanStack or TanStack AI code, follow the matching mappings in `AGENTS.md`.
Before editing TanStack AI code, load the bundled guidance with:

```bash
bunx @tanstack/intent@latest load @tanstack/ai#ai-core
```
